\par }\pard\plain \s16\qj \li454\ri0\sb240\sa120\sl360\slmult1\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin454\itap0\pararsid14049678 \b\f36\fs18\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f0\fs28\insrsid5640755 One Example of Perfect Creation
